### NotificationService API Testing
### Local: http://localhost:5089
### Kubernetes: http://<node-ip>:30082

@NotificationService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5089
@K8s_HostAddress = http://localhost:30082

### Health Check
GET {{NotificationService_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Notification Statistics
GET {{NotificationService_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Send Notification to User (Immediate)
POST {{NotificationService_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user1",
  "subject": "Test Notification",
  "message": "This is a test notification sent via API!"
}

###

