###

### Get Pending Notifications
GET {{NotificationService_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/pending
Accept: application/json

###

### Schedule Notification for Future Delivery
POST {{NotificationService_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/schedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user1",
  "userEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "userName": "John Doe",
  "type": 3,
  "subject": "Book Due Soon Reminder",
  "message": "<p>Your book 'The Great Gatsby' is due in 2 days. Please return it on time.</p>",
  "bookId": 1,
  "borrowingRecordId": 1,
  "scheduledFor": "2025-01-10T09:00:00Z"
}

